Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit digital landscape split down the middle - on the left, a towering vertical stack of glowing rectangular containers piled high like a monolithic inbox tower, each compartment sealed and orderly with sharp geometric edges, bathed in cold blue light. On the right, a flowing horizontal river of holographic data streams cascading endlessly forward like luminous water, fragments of information dissolving and reforming in warm pink and orange hues. Rain falls between the two paradigms, creating reflections on a dark chrome floor. The contrast between rigid vertical structure and fluid horizontal motion creates dramatic tension, with small hovering drones navigating between both systems. The atmosphere is moody with volumetric fog and lens flares from distant city lights in the background.
